              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>A machine created from the union between Fontaine's intricate device and special energy technologies. Based on whether it's imbued with <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">ousia or pneuma</span> energy, the machine will operate differently in battle. When either energy is annihilated upon being <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">attacked by its opposite</span>, an Overloaded state will be induced, causing the machine to lose energy and its combat capabilities.</p>"
